author: Russell Brand
description:
Bobby Kennedy claims the CDC covered up a study showing an 1100% increase in autism from the Hep B vaccine. Now, as head of the HHS, he’s removing aluminum from shots — and Big Pharma’s furious. In this stream, I look at what’s behind the vaccine panic, whether the suppression of this data was deliberate, and whether the new HHS leadership marks a real change. Let me know what you think in the comments and chat.
